contents: As lots of you guys commented (See below!) on my first play of The Wave by Sorrontis, my strategy was clearly sub optimal. Therefore, I did revisit The Wave, to ride it better this time. Sometimes the optimal strategy may not be obvious from the start as the creeper behaves different than expected e.g. the speed, quantity, and strength of the creeper in this mission were slower, more and harder than I expected in the first run.
